lead_paragraph: Jason Day pulled out of the Olympics on Tuesday because of the Zika virus, costing golf its No. 1 player as it returns from a century-long absence at the games.

headline.print_headline: Top-Ranked Jason Day Skipping Rio Olympics Because of Zika
